'''2015年查塔努加槍擊案'''，是指發生於2015年7月16日，在[[美國|美國]][[田納西州|田納西州]][[查塔努加_(田納西州)|查塔努加]]的兩處軍事設施的槍擊案，共造成包括槍手在內的6人死亡，4名是[[美國海軍陸戰隊|美國海軍陸戰隊]]隊員<ref name=nbc1 />，另一人是海軍士官，另有2人受傷。槍手[[穆罕默德·尤瑟夫·阿卜杜阿齊茲|穆罕默德·尤瑟夫·阿卜杜阿齊茲]]（Muhammad Youssef Abdulazeez）在第二案發現場被擊斃<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wjhl.com/2015/07/16/shooting-reported-near-campus-of-chattanooga-state-community-college/|title=Gunman kills four Marines in attacks at military recruiting centers in Chattanooga|work=WJHL|date=July 16, 2015|accessdate=July 16, 2015|archive-date=2015-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717045238/http://wjhl.com/2015/07/16/shooting-reported-near-campus-of-chattanooga-state-community-college/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而本案已朝[[國內恐怖主義|國內恐怖主義]]的方向調查<ref name=FourMarines /><ref name="ChattanoogaShootings">{{cite web|url=http://news.yahoo.com/chattanooga-active-shooter-officer-down-live-coverage-154953657.html|title=Shootings at Chattanooga military facilities leave 4 Marines, gunman dead|work=Yahoo! News|date=July 16, 2015|accessdate=July 16, 2015|archive-date=2015-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150716230409/http://news.yahoo.com/chattanooga-active-shooter-officer-down-live-coverage-154953657.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 行兇者 ==
24歲的枪手阿卜杜阿齐兹出生於[[科威特|科威特]]，在一個保守的[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]家庭長大。他自小隨家人移居美國，住在田納西州的查塔努加，並归化入籍成為美国公民。2012年，他在查塔努加[[田納西大學|田納西大學]]取得工程學學位畢業。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/chattanooga-shooter-came-from-middle-class-muslim-family/2015/07/16/815c39c2-2c04-11e5-bd33-395c05608059_story.html |title=Chattanooga gunman came from a middle-class Muslim family |publisher=The [[Washington_Post|Washington Post]] |date=2015-07-16 |accessdate=2015-07-17 |archive-date=2017-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102115824/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/chattanooga-shooter-came-from-middle-class-muslim-family/2015/07/16/815c39c2-2c04-11e5-bd33-395c05608059_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

阿卜杜阿齐兹的父親曾經被美國當局列入恐怖主义嫌疑人监控名单，不過後來被剔除。阿卜杜阿齐兹事前未有被當局列為監控對象。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20150717/c17tennessee/dual/ |title=美国田纳西州四名海军陆战队员被枪杀 |work=纽约时报中文网 |date=2015-07-17 |accessdate=2015-07-17 |archive-date=2015-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721063820/http://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20150717/c17tennessee/dual |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 經過 ==
7月16日，枪手在查塔努加市一个购物中心边开车，边向位于购物中心的军方徵兵中心开枪，枪手总共开了25到30枪，一名海军陆战队徵兵官员腿部中弹受伤。

枪手接着开车到大约10公里之外海军後備役中心。他开枪扫射，中心内的四名海军陆战队士兵被槍殺。枪击停止后，枪手也已经死亡。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.voachinese.com/content/us-military-shooting-20150716/2866013.html |title=美国4名海军陆战队队员在田纳西州军事设施内被枪杀 |publisher=美國之音 |date=2015-07-17 |accessdate=2015-07-17 |archive-date=2015-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717055331/http://www.voachinese.com/content/us-military-shooting-20150716/2866013.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>另一名中槍的海軍士官延至7月18日不治。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-33580151 |title=Chattanooga attack: Fifth victim dies from wounds |work=BBC News |date=2015-07-18 |accessdate=2015-07-19 |archive-date=2015-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150718140157/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-33580151 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

